{"tid":1696890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朝日電視台報導河妖事件，指出網絡上有聲音指\"自作自演\"","createTime":"2019-11-06T12:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T14:28:12.000Z","uid":51271,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"11a68ca01e28d787799399d919197d217d7ff340","tid":1696890,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:53:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1Z8kvlua0eg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1Z8kvlua0eg&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=b3e23cf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1Z8kvlua0eg</a><br />\n<br />\n香港の区議会選挙に立候補している男性が刃物で襲われた瞬間の映像です。<br />\n<br />\n 香港で選挙活動をする候補者に花束を持った男が話し掛けています。ネット上に流された映像では男が一緒に写真を撮ろうと声を掛けてかばんから携帯を取り出すそぶりを見せた次の瞬間、男は突然、刃物で候補者の男性の左胸を刺したと現地メディアは伝えました。男性の命に別状はありません。刺した男はすぐ取り押えられました。<strong>ネット上では事件が自作自演だという指摘が上がる</strong>など、選挙を巡っても対立が深まっています。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另有反蒙面法一個月+區選小特輯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ARfm9wR-26k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DARfm9wR-26k&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=863b5b99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ARfm9wR-26k</a>"},{"pid":"32c52d5700c5334a28d4ad743070355cd80df241","tid":1696890,"uid":16109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"721桶咗個大頭佛，而家想係咁宜吉一吉帶罪立工就便宜咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7735be79a74bed3f4d9b8ca75567ecc434f45fe","tid":1696890,"uid":70127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b574f249414aa3ae9b18f5030614723c0236e65","tid":1696890,"uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T1